                            "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01znq?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-145-Hellknight-Hill"
                        },
                        "page": 91
                    }
                ],
                "subtype": "sidebar",
                "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
                "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Tixitogs live long lives, and they have cultivated knowledge over the years that may prove useful for adventurers who can coax it from them. A tixitog who has been bested in combat will not mindlessly fight to the death, but will instead try to strike a deal with its attackers, speaking in simple Common to offer information, treasure, or even the aid of its spider-herding abilities under the right circumstances."
            }
        ],
